": "Edit: {'replace_all': False, 'file_path': '/Users/sasha/IdeaProjects/personal_projects, {'replace_all': False, 'file_path': '/Users/sasha/IdeaProjects/personal_projects", "files": ["{'replace_all': False, 'file_path': '/Users/sasha/IdeaProjects/personal_projects", "{'replace_all': False, 'file_path': '/Users/sasha/IdeaProjects/personal_projects"], "tokens": 0, "duration_ms": 0}, {"type": "verify", "timestamp": 1774725922.141515, "detail": "Verify: {'command': 'uv run pytest tests/unit/test_idle_agent_recycling.py -x -q 2>&1', ", "files": ["{'command': 'uv run pytest tests/unit/test_idle_agent_recycling.py -x -q 2>&1', "], "tokens": 0, "duration_ms": 0}, {"type": "plan", "timestamp": 1774725923.2735906, "detail": "Plan: ", "files": [], "tokens": 0, "duration_ms": 0}, {"type": "verify", "timestamp": 1774725924.4056659, "detail": "Verify: {'command': 'uv run pytest tests/unit/test_crash_recovery.py tests/unit/test_age", "files": ["{'command': 'uv run pytest tests/unit/test_crash_recovery.py tests/unit/test_age"], "tokens": 0, "duration_ms": 0}, {"type": "plan", "timestamp": 1774725925.5377414, "detail": "Plan: ", "files": [], "tokens": 0, "duration_ms": 0}, {"type": "verify", "timestamp": 1774725926.669817, "detail": "Verify: {'command': 'curl -s --retry 3 --retry-delay 2 --retry-all-errors -X POST http:/", "files": ["{'command': 'curl -s --retry 3 --retry-delay 2 --retry-all-errors -X POST http:/"], "tokens": 0, "duration_ms": 0}, {"type": "plan", "timestamp": 1774725927.8018923, "detail": "Plan: {'todos': [{'content': 'Add recycle_idle_agents() to agent_lifecycle.py', 'statu", "files": ["{'todos': [{'content': 'Add recycle_idle_agents() to agent_lifecycle.py', 'statu"], "tokens": 0, "duration_ms": 0}, {"type": "complete", "timestamp": 1774725934.988696, "detail": "Agent exited with outcome: success", "files": [], "tokens": 0, "duration_ms": 346028}], "outcome": "success", "log_path": "/Users/sasha/IdeaProjects/personal_projects/bernstein/.sdd/runtime/backend-b6050c9b.log", "task_snapshots": [{"id": "60d4927c02b1", "title": "[RETRY 1] 333g \u2014 Idle Agent Detection and Recycling", "description": "[retry:1] **Depends on:** #742\n\n## Problem\n\nAgents that finish their task don't always exit cleanly. They sometimes sit idle consuming a slot. Or they're stuck in a loop making no file changes. The orchestrator needs to detect these and recycle the slot.\n\n## Design\n\n### Idle detection (already partially exists in #500)\nAn agent is \"idle\" if:\n- Process is alive but no file changes for 120s\n- Process is alive but no heartbeat update for 90s\n- Task is marked \"done\" or \"failed\" on server but process still running\n\n### Recycling\nWhen idle detected:\n1. Send SHUTDOWN signal (#736)\n2. Wait 30s\n3. If still alive \u2192 SIGKILL\n4. Mark agent slot as free\n5. Log: \"Recycled idle agent backend-abc123 (no activity for 2min)\"\n\n### Aggressive mode for self-development\nWhen `--evolve` is active, idle threshold drops to 60s. Self-development needs fast agent turnover.\n\n## Files to modify\n\n- `src/bernstein/core/orchestrator.py` (idle detection in tick)\n- `src/bernstein/core/agent_lifecycle.py` (recycling logic)\n\n## Completion signal\n\n- Idle agents detected and killed within 2 minutes\n- Freed slots immediately used for new tasks\n- No zombie agents consuming resources", "role": "backend", "priority": 0, "scope": "medium", "complexity": "medium", "estimated_minutes": 60, "status": "open", "task_type": "standard", "upgrade_details": null, "depends_on": [], "completion_signals": [], "owned_files": [], "assigned_agent": null, "result_summary": null, "cell_id": null, "repo": null, "model": "sonnet", "effort": "high", "mcp_servers": [], "created_at": 1774725535.413523, "progress_log": [], "version": 1}]}
